query:
SELECT
            COALESCE(SUM(review_duration_ms), 0) as "total_time!: i64",
            COUNT(*) as "total_cards!: i64",
            COALESCE(AVG(CAST(review_duration_ms AS REAL)), 0.0) as "avg_time!: f64"
        FROM review_history
        WHERE review_duration_ms IS NOT NULL
            AND reviewed_at >= ?
            AND reviewed_at <= ?
